The '''imperial election of April 1, 1257''' was an [[imperial election]] held to select the [[Holy Roman Emperor|emperor]] of the [[Holy Roman Empire]].

As a result of the election, [[Alfonso X of Castile]] was named [[Holy Roman Emperor]].

