'''L’Ajuntaera pa la Plática, l'Esturrie y l'Escarculle la Llengua Murciana'''{{efn|Murcian pronunciation: {{IPA-esdia|lɑ̟χu̞n̪ˈt̪æ̯e̞ɾɑ̟ pɑ̟ lɑ̟ ˈplɑ̟t̪i̞kɑ̟, lɛˈt̪ːu̞rje̞ j ˌlɛkːɑ̟ɾˈku̞ʎe̞ː lɑ̟ ˈʎe̞ŋgʊ̯ɑ̟ mu̞ɾˈθjɑ̟nɑ̟|}}}} (''La Asociación para el Habla, la Difusión y el Desarrollo de la Lengua Murciana'' in [[Spanish language|Spanish]]) is a cultural association which seeks expansion of the [[Murcian Spanish|Murcian language]], considering it as a separate language, as well as research of the language. It also seeks to help any people who want to speak or write the language. The number of members as well as the activities they promote (besides their own web) is unknown. No activities are known in the last years in [[Murcia]], where it is supposed to have its headquarters.

