'''''Le Quotidien d'Oran''''' ({{lang-ar|لو كوتيديان دوران}}; {{ISSN|1111-2166}}) is a daily French-language Algerian newspaper, headquartered in [[Oran]], [[Algeria]].<ref>"[http://www.lequotidien-oran.com/index.php?action=contact Contact]." ''Le Quotidien d'Oran''. Retrieved on 7 December 2015. "1 rue Laid Ould Tayeb 63 avenue de l’ANP Oran-Algérie B.P N°110"</ref>

It was established on 14 December 1994.{{fact|date=December 2015}}

The editor is [[Kamel Daoud]]. The column "Raïna Raïkoum" ("My Opinion, Your Opinion") is written by Daoud.<ref>Daoud, Kamel. Translated into English by Suzanne Ruta. "[https://www.guernicamag.com/daily/kamel_daoud_meursault/ Kamel Daoud: Meursault]" ([https://www.webcitation.org/6da3RBrIg Archive]). ''[[Guernica (magazine)|Guernica]]''. March 28, 2011. Retrieved on December 7, 2015.</ref>

