{{Infobox country telephone plan | country = Burundi | country_link = Burundi | continent = Africa | map_image = Location_Burundi_AU_Africa.svg | map_caption = Location of Burundi (dark green) | map_size = | map_alt = | country_calling_code = +257 | international_prefix = 00 | trunk_prefix = | regulator = [http://www.arct.gov.bi/ ARCT] | plan_membership = | nsn_length = 8 | dial_plan_type = | number_format = +257 yy yy xxxx | codes_list = }}
==Calling formats== To call in Burundi, the following format is used:
'''yy yy xxxx''' Calls inside Burundi
'''+257 yy yy xxxx''' Calls from outside Burundi
The NSN length is eight digits.
